# Asset Icon Size in ListCell

All asset icons rendered inside a `ListCell` `media` prop must be **32×32px** with a **16px border-radius** (circular).

```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT
media={
  <div style={{ width: 32, height: 32, borderRadius: 16, ... }}>
    <CryptoIcon ... />
  </div>
}

// ❌ WRONG — do not use 36, 40, or any other size
media={
  <div style={{ width: 36, height: 36, borderRadius: 18, ... }}>
    <CryptoIcon ... />
  </div>
}
```

This applies to all asset icon wrappers: `CryptoIcon`, `FiatIcon`, `Icon`, or any custom badge used as a `ListCell` media item.
